             was indicted for <rs id="t18190915-12-off65" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18190915-12-off65" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18190915-12-off65" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18190915-12-cd66" type="crimeDate">13th of September</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18190915-12-off65 t18190915-12-cd66"></join>, one watch, value 20 s.; one chain, value 1 s.; two seals, value 1 s., and two keys, value 6 d., the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18190915-12-victim173" type="victimName">
                           Thomas 
